mber per floor completed + extra drops from Spire bosses","url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-added-4","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"added","text":"Dark Disciple NPC: sells new gear for Umbral Fragments (significant grind; Rebirth Essence useful here)","url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-added-5","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"added","text":"~7 new weapons and ~4 new armor pieces obtainable in the Spire","url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-added-6","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"added","text":"Grimoires: new equip slot (up to 3 equipped at once), class-locked passives \u2014 trade in a full artifact set to receive one","url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-added-7","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"added","text":"Base Class Grimoires: trade in box of origin sets with base class masters in Nevaris","url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-added-8","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"added","text":"New Nevaris map: expanded, prettier, and more optimised (part of ongoing world map refresh by @Polliwagon)","url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-added-9","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"added","text":"Boss lure crafting: craftsman NPC can craft boss lures in exchange for monster memories","url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-added-10","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"added","text":"Vending Search: buy items in stacks of 10 or 100 (hold Ctrl or Shift respectively)","url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-added-11","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"added","text":"New Server Selection UI with region indicators","url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-added-12","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"added","text":"Click to Move toggle: disables the default click/hold-to-move character movement","url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-changed-0","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"changed","text":"Essence rarity order changed to Flow > Growth > Destruction > Rebirth > Chaos (rebalances Chaos imbalance)","url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-changed-1","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"changed","text":"Chaos essence: implicit swap removed \u2014 higher chance for other options, much lower chance of nothing happening on non-weapons","url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-changed-2","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"changed","text":"Rebirth essence: can now lock a stat while randomising the others (additional use case alongside original re-roll)","url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-changed-3","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"changed","text":"Autocast reduced across the board: 20% \u2192 10% and 30% \u2192 20%; headgear autocast cards are now unique","url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-changed-4","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"changed","text":"Bolts / Meteor / Chain Lightning autocast damage unnerfed: 50% \u2192 100%","url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-changed-5","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"changed","text":"Status damage reduced: divisor /8 \u2192 /10 (~20% reduction)","url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-changed-6","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"changed","text":"Scrap Fang: Slots 4 \u2192 3, Multistrike 100% \u2192 50%","url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-changed-7","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"changed","text":"Launcher: Slots 4 \u2192 3","url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-changed-8","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"changed","text":"Siphon reclassified as leech \u2014 recovery over time, capped at 20% HP/MP (was instant)","url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-changed-9","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"changed","text":"Perfect Dodge: no longer scales with AGI, hard-capped at 95%","url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-changed-10","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"changed","text":"Auto attacks can no longer hit the same target multiple times (fixes Launcher/Shotgun splash + chain overlap)","url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-changed-11","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"changed","text":"Bosses recover 10% HP per second when out of combat (was 100% HP instantly)","url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-changed-12","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"changed","text":"Shadow Step: cooldown 2 \u2192 7 seconds (\u22121 per skill level)","url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-changed-13","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"changed","text":"Sniper Shot: damage 150% \u2192 200%","url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-changed-14","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"changed","text":"Bosses: faster cast times, adjusted cooldowns, more targeted attacks, now spawn giant minions","url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-changed-15","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"changed","text":"Shadow Step, Fireball, Ice Shard, Damnation, HolyWrath, Piercing Shot, and Sniper Shot can now be cast as either targeted or ground-targeted","url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-changed-16","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"changed","text":"Utility items: Def/MDef stats replaced with weight limit per refine","url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-changed-17","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"changed","text":"Monster flat Def scaling reduced: VIT/2 \u2192 VIT/5 (less impact on classes like Gunslinger)","url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-changed-18","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"changed","text":"Atk% is now a separate multiplier (slightly more effective than before)","url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-changed-19","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"changed","text":"Loot UI: moved and no longer clickable","url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-changed-20","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"changed","text":"Cursor is now frozen during drag-rotation","url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-fixed-0","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"fixed","text":"Skill mods not applying to summons","url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-fixed-1","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"fixed","text":"Sacred Aegis not being refreshed correctly","url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-fixed-2","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"fixed","text":"Several issues with monster leap attacks","url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"},{"id":"v0.17.0-removed-0","version":"0.17.0","patch_title":"The Echoing Spire","date":"2026-05-25","type":"removed","text":"Hidden 100% Multistrike removed from Naga, Bat, and Wolf gear","url":"/patch/?v=0.17.0"}]}